                    <span>I am fairly new to load balancing, and this book provided an almost perfect introduction to the topic.<P>From a technical writing point-of-view, this is probably one of the best written books I have ever come across. The chapters are well organzied and are fairly easy to follow. Complex topics are clearly explained. The use of diagrams is very good as well.<P>If you want to learn more about load balancing, buy this book.</span>
                  
              
